B3-2/poem-IGETeQBwf_c0CasyF8dTBQ">Như mộng lệnh kỳ 2 - 如夢令其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/author-6q8syMJi1LKPt3rH8HfbQQ">Lý Thanh Chiếu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ki%E1%BB%87t/Ph%E1%BA%A1t-T%E1%BB%91ng-l%E1%BB%99-b%E1%BB%91-v%C4%83n/poem-grqwKCBlZO2da-xlEa8EqQ">Phạt Tống lộ bố văn - 伐宋露布文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ki%E1%BB%87t/author-k8EDHIxplIZZ0LYB28XrSA">Lý Thường Kiệt</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Thanh-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/T%C3%A2n-gia-ba-tr%C3%BAc-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-4he4H7e1fZEK5aRJcCxa3A">Tân-gia-ba trúc chi từ kỳ 1 - 新嘉波竹枝詞其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Thanh-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/author-H7U7KCvecgO1KzCd1kGc9A">Phan Thanh Giản</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%E1%BA%A3nh/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C3%AA-c%C3%B4ng-N%C4%83ng-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/poem-XLo5tVTB-4Np8PsqkM_n8g">Tống Lê công Năng Nhượng - 送黎公能讓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%E1%BA%A3nh/author-rNqdNPS8u7Eq1xJT55nc6A">Trần Cảnh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
